            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Here lies Tarric son of Iohannis, who lived for 3 years, 2 months, 16 days. Laid to rest in peace, the 17th day before the Kalends of January, in the 14th indiction.</p>
